<p><strong><em>Magic Resistance.</em></strong> The pixie has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.</p>

<p><strong><em>Innate Spellcasting.</em></strong> The pixieâ€™s innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 12). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring only its pixie dust as a component:</p>

<p>At will: druidcraft</p>

<p>1/day each: confusion, dancing lights, detect evil and good, detect thoughts, dispel magic, entangle, fly, phantasmal force, polymorph, sleep</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Superior Invisibility.</em></strong> The pixie magically turns invisible until its concentration ends (as if concentrating on a spell). Any equipment the pixie wears or carries is invisible with it.</p>

